                    <h4><strong>Contraindications</strong></h4>
                    <p class="text-justify">Levocetirizine is contraindicated in patients with severe renal impairment, hypersensitivity to Levocetirizine, piperazine derivatives or to any ingredient in the formulation. For Levocetirizine no data on exposed human pregnancy is available. Hence it should be used in pregnancy only when the benefits to the mother outweigh the risk to the fetus. Use of Levocetirizine in lactating women is not recommended as it is expected to be excreted in breast milk.</p>
